<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="support-n">support <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /sə'pɔːt/    美 /sə'pɔːrt/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>支撑物；支持：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>These wooden supports help to hold up the building.
这些木制支架有助于稳固建筑。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I depend on my friends for emotional support. 
我依赖朋友给我情感支持。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>资助；赡养：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Her job is the family’s only means of support. 
她家全靠她的工作来维持生计。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-support-of">in support of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>支持；证明：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He made some experiments in support of his own idea. 
他做了一些实验来证明自己的观点。</p></div></div>